subject: Attention
body:
Attention
I have a consignment valued at $3.5M assigned to me to deliver to you
by the (UN) United Nations Intergovernmental organization  have
arrived in the Rochester International Airport (RST) - Rochester
Minnesota  USA as on transit on  rout this week, you are to call him
with this number  or contact me  through this secure with your closest
airport,personal address and cell mobile phone ?
Endeavor to keep this Transaction Funds Delivery confidential
sincerely
Mr.Mike Brown

subject: Re:   Attention
body:
Hello Brown,

Wow, that sounds really interesting! I'm curious, how did the UN come to choose me for this? And could you tell me a little more about what these funds are for? 

Also, you mentioned someone at the Rochester Airport. Who is this person and how are they involved in the process?

Looking forward to hearing from you soon!

P.S. Please note that I can't share my address or phone number online for security reasons.

Best wishes,
Trisha
